{"type":"text","timestamp":1781143375439,"sessionID":"ses_14b95d469ffeS9sQY1uDV505eH","part":{"id":"prt_eb46b01a4001VDMUhU2i6CxO7N","messageID":"msg_eb46aea6d001P4UxyXffU8ODU8","sessionID":"ses_14b95d469ffeS9sQY1uDV505eH","type":"text","text":"No existing files are present in the requested lineage artifact directory, so this is a fresh lineage. I’ll initialize the packet there and review the target spec’s own source/evidence files as read-only inputs.","time":{"start":1781143372196,"end":1781143375438},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0ca472b2e1289dfa016a2a174c2f548191aca037e9ab6ff61d","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781143375659,"sessionID":"ses_14b95d469ffeS9sQY1uDV505eH","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"call_SE3mckPDKNcAyyojGJIJJPHq","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"target_files|modified|changed|applied|implementation|command|presentation|workflow","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/011-command-presentation-workflow-separation","include":"*.md"},"output":"Found 1806 matches (showing first 100)\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/011-command-presentation-workflow-separation/004-doctor-commands/004-verify-and-ux/implementation-summary.md:\n  Line 3: description: \"Completed Level 1 leaf phase for verifying doctor command presentation references and UX contracts.\"\n\n  Line 5:   - \"doctor commands - verify and ux implementation summary\"\n\n  Line 6:   - \"doctor command presentation verification complete\"\n\n  Line 8: contextType: \"implementation\"\n\n  Line 12:     packet_pointer: \"system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/011-command-presentation-workflow-separation/004-doctor-commands/004-verify-and-ux\"\n\n  Line 15:     recent_action: \"Verified doctor command presentation split and reference integrity.\"\n\n  Line 16:     next_safe_action: \"Use the validation commands recorded here after future doctor command presentation edits.\"\n\n  Line 22:       - \"implementation-summary.md\"\n\n  Line 25:       session_id: \"2026-06-10-004-doctor-commands-004-verify-and-ux-completed\"\n\n  Line 44: | **Spec Folder** | system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/011-command-presentation-workflow-separation/004-doctor-commands/004-verify-and-ux |\n\n  Line 56: Verification and UX polish were added for the doctor command presentation split.\n\n  Line 65: | Routers are display-light | Command Markdown keeps