or $ARGUMENTS        |\n\n  Line 295: **Inputs:** `$ARGUMENTS` — agent path, optional mode suffix, optional spec folder, optional iteration count\n\n  Line 301: $ARGUMENTS\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/commands/deep/start-context-loop.md:\n  Line 3: argument-hint: \"<scope> [:auto|:confirm] [--max-iterations=N] [--convergence=N] [--executor=<type> [--model=X] [--prompt-framework=X] [--label=X] ...] [--executors=<json>] [--concurrency=N] (:auto supports PRE-BOUND SETUP ANSWERS: prompt-body block for non-interactive setup)\"\n\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 138 matches (38 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":138,"truncated":true},"title":"User request: \\{\\{args\\}\\}|\\$ARGUMENTS|argument-hint","time":{"start":1781143414981,"end":1781143414993}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0263a7a7511abec6016a2a1776dcb88191a52620e66d93adb4"}},"id":"prt_eb46ba8c4001U1ohjaeGhxc66Y","sessionID":"ses_14b95d469ffeS9sQY1uDV505eH","messageID":"msg_eb46b7d3b001vvcQ92eswQH40i"}}
